9 showed that the percentage of Catholics has decreased overall, from 72.9% to 68.3%, in a period of seven years.<ref name=\"CIS2018\" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.eldiario.es/cv/Apostatar-Espana-tramite-via-crucis_0_975702611.html|title=Apostatar en Espa\u00f1a, \u00bftr\u00e1mite o v\u00eda crucis?|website=eldiario.es|language=es|access-date=2019-12-21}}</ref>\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|+Religion by Spanish autonomous communities (%)<ref>http://www.lavanguardia.com/vangdata/20150402/54429637154/interactivo-creencias-y-practicas-religiosas-en-espana.html</ref><ref name=CIS2019detalle>{{Cite web|url=http://www.cis.es/cis/opencm/ES/1_encuestas/estudios/listaMuestras.jsp?estudio=14473 |author=''Centro de Investigaciones Sociol\u00f3gicas'' (Centre for Sociological Research)|title=Macrobar\u00f3metro de octubre 2019, Banco de datos |date=October 2019|page=77 |accessdate=4 February 2020 |language=Spanish}}</ref>\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\" | Region\n! colspan=\"2\" | Catholic<br/><small>Practicing and non-practicing</small>\n! colspan=\"2\" |Other\n! colspan=\"2\" | Unaffiliated \n(Atheism/Agnosticism)\n! colspan=\"2\" | Unanswered\n! rowspan=\"2\" | References\n|-\n!2012\n!2019\n!2012\n!2019\n!2012\n!2019\n!2012\n!2019\n|- style=\"background:#f0f8ff;\"\n| style=\"text-align:left\" | {{flagicon|Murcia}} [[Region of Murcia|Murcia]]\n| 85.0\n|80.1\n| 0.8\n|2.1\n| 13.9\n|17.9\n| 0.3\n|0\n|<ref name=CIS2019Murcia>{{Cite web|url=http://www.cis.es/cis/export/sites/default/-Archivos/Marginales/3260_3279/3263/Marginales/es3263mar_Murcia.pdf |author=''Centro de Investigaciones Sociol\u00f3gicas'' (Centre for Sociological Research)|title=Macrobar\u00f3metro de octubre 2019, Banco de datos - Document 'Poblaci\u00f3n con derecho a voto en elecciones generales y residente en Espa\u00f1a, Regi\u00f3n de Murcia (aut.) |date=October 2019|page=22 |accessdate=4 February 2020 |language=Spanish}}</ref>\n|- style=\"background:#f0f8ff;\"\n| style=\"text-alig